      "role": "user",
      "content": "so i was at this dinner last night and it was like really intense. i dont know how else to describe it but when my coworker was telling this story about his weekend, i could actually feel this weird vibration in my chest everytime he was being fake. it was like a specific pitch or frequency that just felt... off. like his voice was literally out of tune with what he was actually saying. has anyone else ever experienced that?",
